name: Divided /ˈɛnədʒi/
description:
“Everything is about energy. The way you feel around certain people will tell you if this connection needs to be stopped or not. If you give positive vibes, you will get the positive energy, but it can be the other way around. So know your surrounding, know your energy. Let your unique awesomeness and positive energy inspire confidence in others.” 
Artwork by @Baimtje | Music by @pendo46
